column5: Good Choices! How much did you get the Citica for?
You have to ask Santa.      ($89.99 at Gagnon's, doorcrasher on Dec 1)
I don't think that I could sleep on that bed. Is that for when you're in the dog house?
That's more fishing equipment then a man should be allowed in one year....someone must of been extra good this year...
I didn't get any actual fishing gear for Christmas, but my wife renewed my outdoors card for 3 years..   I thought that was pretty thoughtful.
Nice Haul Jer !! I got a spooling station, some Rapala Lures, a new waterproof Camera, a cordless filleting knife, and Sail Gift cards
